{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/notes/one-week-new-ipod-classic/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"One week with the new iPod classic","date":"2007-09-14T00:00:00.000Z","date_pretty":"September 14th, 2007","date_from_now":"13 years ago","last_modified_at":"2013-05-03T00:00:00.000Z","last_modified_at_from_now":"7 years ago","path":"/notes/one-week-new-ipod-classic/","author":null,"excerpt":"Quick impressions of the new iPod classic 60GB.","tags":["Apple","review"],"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.4248704663212435,"src":"/static/6730ab0c074cd50d2e5faf0bd8726d7c/fc20c/ipod-classic-packaging.jpg","srcSet":"/static/6730ab0c074cd50d2e5faf0bd8726d7c/6e883/ipod-classic-packaging.jpg 275w,\n/static/6730ab0c074cd50d2e5faf0bd8726d7c/a09ef/ipod-classic-packaging.jpg 550w,\n/static/6730ab0c074cd50d2e5faf0bd8726d7c/fc20c/ipod-classic-packaging.jpg 1100w,\n/static/6730ab0c074cd50d2e5faf0bd8726d7c/356ef/ipod-classic-packaging.jpg 1280w","sizes":"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px"},"fixed":{"src":"/static/6730ab0c074cd50d2e5faf0bd8726d7c/fc20c/ipod-classic-packaging.jpg","height":770,"width":1100}}},"toc":null,"comments":null,"comments_locked":null,"hide_meta":null},"id":"6f4bab00-e662-5780-a6ca-3374f1f6cb6b","html":"<p>Last week Apple finally unveiled a new generation of iPods. The last iPod I purchased was a 3rd generation model with 40GB of hard drive space and have been waiting for a decent successor. My iTunes Music Library has finally outgrown the 3rd gen so I decided this was the time to get a replacement. I figured an iPod that resembled the iPhone would be just around the corner and pleasantly surprised when the <em>iPod touch</em> was announced.</p>\n<p>At 16GB the iPod touch doesn’t meet my needs, so I decided to go with the new iPod classic 80GB model. Hopefully by then flash drive prices comes down and I can get a version of the iPod touch with 80GB+. Until then the classic more than meets what I was looking for in a music player that can hold all my tunes and have enough juice for a full work day.</p>\n<p>The classic has a few issues, but nothing that has given me buyer’s remorse.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 1100px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.9090909090909%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n        alt=\"iPod classic syncing next to a 40GB iPod\"\n        title=\"iPod classic syncing next to a 40GB iPod\"\n        data-src=\"/static/eb8368553a3a88bdbe787a70fbc74083/eacc7/ipod-classic-syncing.jpg\"\n        data-srcset=\"/static/eb8368553a3a88bdbe787a70fbc74083/16841/ipod-classic-syncing.jpg 275w,\n/static/eb8368553a3a88bdbe787a70fbc74083/50c97/ipod-classic-syncing.jpg 550w,\n/static/eb8368553a3a88bdbe787a70fbc74083/eacc7/ipod-classic-syncing.jpg 1100w,\n/static/eb8368553a3a88bdbe787a70fbc74083/533d0/ipod-classic-syncing.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 1100px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.54545454545455%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n        alt=\"iPod classic thickness compared to an old 40GB iPod\"\n        title=\"iPod classic thickness com